{"tid":1254709,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於近日事件停一停 ，諗一諗","createTime":"2019-06-24T08:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T08:55:47.000Z","uid":264950,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"452d54671cd03d884ac026a19a968e5a74d157e1","tid":1254709,"uid":264950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:52:22.000Z","msg":"小弟初入連登，若果廢話多或講錯，請多多包涵。<br />\n現今形勢，之前616小勝，但621係慘敗。<br />\n慘敗原因係亂啟戰端，我唔係話唔應該搞，而係覺得準備不足。當日點解輸？個人認為備戰方案唔夠周詳。所謂知彼知己，百戰不殆。人地玩閉門戰，一時冇措，轉攻其他地方，之後冇計可施，到處施額，敵人就知道你得一招可以用。死守到完場，再派人宣傳。雖然朋友們辛苦了，但換來反效果。<br />\n<br />\n到左今日，更加陷入苦戰，反噬效果加劇。<br />\n<br />\n我發post唔係話怪責能力不足，而係需要檢討。我覺得要凖備幾個方案才好行動。不是怕人善忘而不斷開啟戰端，每日去一次，人似終體力有限，如果得不到效果更士氣低落。<br />\n<br />\n另外，雖然連登食客三千，可能有好plan...但人地keep住update你地d方案。就算孔明諗到絕世好計，post出來只會俾人預先防備。諗方法整個group，隔絕間諜。<br />\n<br />\n為自由加油!"},{"pid":"99a25f4f8e233ff8bfe817b05c55ee4be6415c49","tid":1254709,"uid":264950,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:55:20.000Z","msg":"多錯別字，岩岩睇到，多多包涵<br />\n<br />\n一時失措<br />\n施壓"},{"pid":"339fa2c8f51561dec24163a71bb8efefe9096be4","tid":1254709,"uid":202730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:55:47.000Z","msg":"急 召日本巴絲或者用開twitter巴絲<br />\n可以推廣到去日本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做好文宣<br />\n<br />\n粵語<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Iwxt5qH2Vto\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIwxt5qH2Vto&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVK%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=80003538\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Iwxt5qH2Vto</a><br />\n<br />\n日文<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KH4FjILxiUM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKH4FjILxiUM&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVK%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=e8b1b158\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KH4FjILxiUM</a><br />\n<br /